name: Jetmobile
overview: A game of the infamous "Cassette 50" collection. Also published in Digital Marketing PD #229. You are a Jet-powered caterpillar and have to eat as many lettuce leaves as possible in 2 minutes. You must not bite yourself or run into the side of the box, which also contains a hungry blackbird. Extra points are given for the length of time you last. Basically a glorified Snake clone
